      No particular niche. No posting schedule. No comments section.
    </p>

    <h2>Who</h2>

    <p>
      <!-- Add your bio here -->
      I'm a person on the internet. Update this section with whatever you want people to know.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>

    <p>
      <!-- Add your contact info here -->
      You can reach me at <a href="mailto:you@example.com">you@example.com</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>This site</h2>

    <p>
      Built with <a href="https://astro.build" rel="noopener noreferrer">Astro</a>,
      hosted on GitHub Pages. Posts are plain Markdown files in the repo.
      No tracking, no ads, no JavaScript except for the dark mode toggle.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
